flowchart TD
    A0["Approach 0: Full Context Dump\nProvide every past thing as context.\nWorks initially. Remembers everything."]
    B0["Bottleneck\nContext grows huge, chat hangs.\nRetrieval from long texts becomes difficult,\nimportant things get lost or de-prioritized."]
    A1["Approach 1: Sliding Window\nTake only the past N messages as context\nand keep this sliding window.\nUses recent and updated info, avoids long context issues."]
    B1["Bottleneck\nDiscards old conversation altogether.\nImportant things in old conversations are lost.\nLeads to results not aligned with initial plans."]
    A2["Approach 2: Naive Retrieval and Semantic Similarity\nExtract and store key nuggets (decisions, updates).\nEmbed incoming requests and stored nuggets.\nRetrieve relevant info via semantic similarity search."]
    B2["Bottleneck\nNaive retrieval, everything extracted gets stored (no write-side judgment).\nSimilarity-only ranking, no extra importance for recency\nor how often something has been useful.\nNo mechanism to handle conflicts or ambiguity."]
    D["Derived Capabilities\nSee first_principles.md"]

    A0 --> B0 --> A1 --> B1 --> A2 --> B2 --> D

    classDef approach0 fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#2563eb,color:#1e3a8a
